    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the engine starts up without issue and provides enough power for standard driving, though it may not have the same responsiveness as a newer model. The transmission shifts reliably, though you might notice some minor vibrations at higher speeds. Cosmetically, there are visible signs of wear and tear, including some minor scratches on the exterior and noticeable upholstery wear in the cabin. It has been maintained to keep it roadworthy, making it a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly, working vehicle.",
      "price": 22500.0,
