    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It has been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with hand-washes every weekend. It looks and drives exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or smudge anywhere! I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale, so I've priced it to move quickly. Come take it for a spin; I promise you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
