      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. The S54 inline-six features a fully overhauled VANOS system and rod bearing replacement for long-term reliability. The engine breathes through individual throttle bodies, delivering razor-sharp throttle response and a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Power is transferred via a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains structurally pristine with a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring zero fatigue under lateral load. Suspension geometry is strictly OEM, featuring fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers to maintain the legendary MacPherson strut and multi-link balance. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example with flawless compression across all cylinders and a dry undercarriage.",
